<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In general if you start a hedge fund and you g=
o into an institutional allocator=E2=80=99s office and say =E2=80=9Cgive me=
 money so I can buy the stocks that will go up,=E2=80=9D they are likely to=
 say to you =E2=80=9Cno, we are full up on people who buy stocks that go up=
, we want returns that are uncorrelated to the stock market.=E2=80=9D And i=
f you go away and put on a fake mustache and come back and say =E2=80=9Cgiv=
e me money so I can buy the bonds that will go up,=E2=80=9D or the commodit=
y futures or the cryptocurrencies or the equity volatility or the distresse=
