 and domestic exchanges using foreknowledge then unknown and undisclosed to=
 Dogecoin investors generally or publicly, of his own intended moves to man=
ipulate the market.=E2=80=9D But his moves were tweets! How can it be illeg=
al insider trading to trade ahead of your own plans to tweet a joke?</p>
</div>
